How to make a distributable archive
===================================


1. ensure you have a working build tree

2. run:

    make distcheck  distdir=lpel-VERSION  DISTCHECK_CONFIGURE_FLAGS="--with-pcl=/path/to/pcl"

for example:

    make distcheck  distdir=lpel-1.x.20111103 DISTCHECK_CONFIGURE_FLAGS="--with-pcl=/usr/local"

3. fix any errors and repeat 2 until it succeeds.

4. retrieve the generated lpel-VERSION.tar.bz2 and distribute.

